<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About the Institute</h1>
        <p>Championing the developmental and cultural interests of the Niger Delta.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: start;">
            <div>
                <h2 style="color: var(--primary-dark); margin-bottom: 25px;">Our History & Mission</h2>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8;">The Institute for Niger Delta Studies (INDS) was established to serve as a high-level research and advocacy center within Niger Delta University. Our mission is to promote the sustainable development of the Niger Delta through rigorous academic research, policy documentation, and community engagement.</p>
                <p style="line-height: 1.8;">We believe that the challenges of the region—environment, economic equity, and social justice—require intellectual solutions grounded in the local context and cultural realities of our people.</p>
                
                <h3 style="margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Institutional Objectives</h3>
                <ul style="list-style: square; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-main);">
                    <li>To conduct and coordinate research into the history, culture, and environment of the Niger Delta.</li>
                    <li>To provide a platform for documentation and preservation of indigenous knowledge systems.</li>
                    <li>To organize conferences, seminars, and memorial lectures (like the Melford Okilo series).</li>
                    <li>To publish the Research Digest, a peer-reviewed academic journal of regional importance.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--bg-soft); padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px;">
                <h3 style="color: var(--primary-dark); margin-bottom: 20px;">Leadership</h3>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                    <img src="/assets/img/prof-sibiri.jpg" alt="Director" style="width: 100px; height: 100px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;">
                    <div>
                        <h4 style="margin: 0;">Prof. A.E. Sibiri</h4>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted);">Director, INDS</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; font-style: italic;">"The Institute stands as a testament to our commitment to ensuring that the voice of the Niger Delta is heard in the halls of global academia."</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
